	* SHOGUN Release 0.1.2
	* compile fixes for R on MaxOSX
	* some compile fixes for cygwin/WIN32
	* Weighted Degree/Weighted Degree Shift kernel speedups & fixes
	* python build fixes
	* initial *workin* swig support 
	* entropy example

